[node name="Notes" type="Node3D" parent="."]

[node name="Note1" type="RigidBody3D" parent="Notes"]
position = Vector3(-6.8, 0.01, -8.4)
mass = 0.01
script = ExtResource("2_holdable")
item_name = "Crumpled Note"
item_id = "note_cars"
readable_text = "Tried the cars.
All dead.

Battery in the dark one
might still have charge—
the lights flickered when
I slammed the door.

Don't bother with
the rust bucket.
Already checked. Twice.

Keep the gate in sight.
Something moves along
the fence line after dark.

  — M"

[node name="CollisionShape3D" type="CollisionShape3D" parent="Notes/Note1"]
shape = SubResource("BoxShape3D_paper")

[node name="MeshInstance3D" type="MeshInstance3D" parent="Notes/Note1"]
mesh = SubResource("BoxMesh_paper")
surface_material_override/0 = SubResource("Mat_paper")

[node name="Note2" type="RigidBody3D" parent="Notes"]
position = Vector3(-17.5, 0.01, -14.0)
mass = 0.01
script = ExtResource("2_holdable")
item_name = "Torn Page"
item_id = "note_signal"
readable_text = "Getting signal on
the radio. Channel 7.
Static, then silence,
then three tones.

Always three tones.

We tried broadcasting
back on day four.

The tones stopped
for six hours.

Then came back louder.

We stopped trying."

[node name="CollisionShape3D" type="CollisionShape3D" parent="Notes/Note2"]
shape = SubResource("BoxShape3D_paper")

[node name="MeshInstance3D" type="MeshInstance3D" parent="Notes/Note2"]
mesh = SubResource("BoxMesh_paper")
surface_material_override/0 = SubResource("Mat_paper")

[node name="Note3" type="RigidBody3D" parent="Notes"]
position = Vector3(1.5, 0.01, 1.6)
mass = 0.01
script = ExtResource("2_holdable")
item_name = "Notepad Leaf"
item_id = "note_journal"
readable_text = "Oct 19

The car horn goes off
by itself. 3am, every
night without fail.

I stopped going to
check on day two.

There is nothing in
the car. I know that.

The footprints this
morning went to the
south fence and just
stopped. No gate open.
No way out."

